name: Guac' a Mole
description: In a swirly, goofy universe so far away it's unlikely to even exist... You are a doomed planet. Hideous avocado mutants are destroying you from the inside, and a persistent meteor rain is raging down on you. To live a little longer and get a high score you must rotate! Then, instead of you, the meteors will hit the mutants when they crawl up from your insides. While doing so you could also look at the beautifully handdrawn universe around you, and listen to the addictive retro-styled music. You know, if you get a spare moment between the meteor hits. Have a blast!
